message: Haha. Deal. I see you're a question asker... I'm an engineer by trade and an entrepreneur by day so I geek out about the stuff. Given that I am in more of a leadership role now, I keep up with tech trends on medium, LaunchTicker, Abundance Insider, ProductHunt, and the CBInsights newsletter. Daily reads for me to keep an eye on trends. When it comes to more technical specifics, I really rely on our engineers here that are way smarter than me on the subject. They frequent (and run) events around town and keep a pulse on new platforms, frameworks, tools, APIs, IDEs, etc. How do YOU keep up with technology?
